ters need women who have courage in order for them to carry out a suicide bombing mission. Asked whether the women who are both jailed for wanting to be suicide bomber regret their action, she said no.” In fact, they seem rather proud of what they had done. They are still radical,” said Rizka."	Terrorism	Terrorism
